Step 1: Start
Step 2: Declare variables
        studyHours, sleepHours, assignments, socialTime, stressScore
Step 3: Input values
        Read studyHours
        Read sleepHours
        Read assignments
        Read socialTime
Step 4: Initialize
        Set stressScore = 0
Step 5: Check study hours
        If studyHours > 8, add 3 to stressScore
        Else if studyHours > 5, add 2
        Else add 1
Step 6: Check sleep hours
        If sleepHours < 5, add 3 to stressScore
        Else if sleepHours < 7, add 2
        Else add 1
Step 7: Check assignments
        If assignments > 5, add 3 to stressScore
        Else if assignments > 2, add 2
        Else add 1
Step 8: Check social/relaxation time
        If socialTime < 1, add 3 to stressScore
        Else if socialTime < 2, add 2
        Else add 1
Step 9: Display stress score
        Print stressScore
Step 10: Determine stress level
        If stressScore <= 5, display LOW
        Else if stressScore <= 9, display MODERATE
        Else display HIGH
Step 11: Stop
